snippet.title: Car Dealer Simulator - Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
🎮 Add to STEAM WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2404880/Car_Dealer_Simulator

Uncover a goldmine in the used car market!
Sniff out deals, buy low, modify, and sell high. Your journey from amateur grease monkey to car dealer magnate awaits.
How fast will you rise in this lucrative venture?
